Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.51,0:00:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要歼灭敌人了哦！
