Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点火！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超  超重力鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全发射管开始进行填装！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…超级质…质子炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…全…全炮门采取发射态势！
